- adwaita-gtk3-theme no longer provides a settings.ini file
- set locale path to /usr/share/locale so that translations may be used
  during install
- try fix auto detect mode tried first
- try modesetting driver last

Version 16.37 - 3 July 2014

- fix /etc/fstab writing (mga#13114, also reported by Joseph Wang)
- partitioning:
  o improve fs sorting in combo box (mga#13640)

Version 16.34.2 -  4 July 2014

- try modesetting before fbdev driver
- try auto detect Xorg settings by default before trying fbdev & vesa drivers
- let udev handle floppies

Version 16.34.1 -  1 July 2014

- default to chrony if found
- fix export of correct distro_release & distro_release_information subroutines
- fix unnecessary '-noleaf' argument passed to 'find' in timezone.pm that
  breaks with busybox implementation
- fix not being able to select packages when list contains only one (mga#13492)

Version 16.33 - 18 June 2014

- stop creating some /dev entries that are managed by udev
- do not even try to create basic /dev nodes

Version 16.32.1 - 15 June 2014

- include platform driver autoload udev rules
- don't keep on mounting a new /tmp/.X11-unix for each time the graphical
  installer would be restarted/crash, just check whether it's already mounted
  first
- fix an inverted conditional which prevents an updated version of /etc/fstab
  to be written

Version 16.32 - 17 June 2014

- in stead of installing only one package per transaction, increase it to 20
  in order to improve install speed
- keep existing entries from /etc/fstab when writing a new
- include the following more "generic"'ish xorg drivers that might come in
  handy if any of the other fails:
	* modesetting_drv.so
	* vboxvideo_drv.so
	* vesa_drv.so
	* vmware_drv.so
	* evdev_drv.so
	* mouse_drv.so
	* kbd_drv.so
	* synaptics_drv.so
	* vmmouse_drv.so
- only complain about missing /boot/efi on EFI systems
- recognize new kernel-3.15 drivers

Version 16.31.1 - 6 June 2014

- include udev rule for VMmouse

Version 16.31 - 6 June 2014

- xorg config:
  o rely on evdev/udev for input devices
  o Wacom tablets should work better
    (we now load the wacom driver again)
  o Synaptics touchpads should now work during install (mga#11524)

Version 16.30 - 4 June 2014

- locale setting
  o update locales list
- drop (broken) support for Alpha, PPC, Sparc & IA64
- add some POD documentation
- do not unavailable kernel-xbox
- change detection order of bootloader so that it'll prioritize in the order
  of grub2 -> grub -> lilo rather than lilo -> grub -> grub2
- in stead of modifying /etc/passwd directly, just simply use 'usermod'
- add support for SHA512
- properly enable nofsync for package installation
- drop (broken) support for Alpha, PPC, Sparc & IA64

Version 16.29 -  3 May 2014

- gnome-icon-theme is now adwaita-icon-theme

