Version 12.5 - 5 March 2009

- handle new drivers
  o dvb: dm1105, dvb-usb-af9015, dvb-usb-cinergyT2, firedtv
  o ethernet: smsc9420
  o gigabit: atl1c
  o pata: cs5536, it8172, it821x
